            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1584989565592-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>orzo</strong> to the <strong>browned chicken</strong> and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add the<strong> stock</strong>, reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 10-15 min, stirring occasionally, until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!), the orzo is tender with a slight bite and most of the liquid has been absorbed</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1584989569307-x200.jpg",
