          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the orzo is cooking, chop the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> into wedges</p><p>Add the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> and<strong> tomato wedges</strong> to a baking tray with the <strong>oregano</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 10-15 min or until softening and starting to burst</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1584989572688-x200.jpg",
