          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Once everything is cooked, add the<strong> soft cheese</strong> and <strong>blitzed spinach </strong>to the orzo and stir it all together</p><p>Tip: Add a splash more boiled water if it looks a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
